N Onyeisi oche Ọhụrụ ndị Ejigbo LCDA bú Hon
Ahọrọ ya na onwa Julaị, na afọ 2017
Enwere mpaghara isii na Ejigbo LCDA: Aigbaka, Ailegun, Fadu, Ifoshi, Ilamose and Oke-Afa ward

Ejigbo-Lagos no na ebe mpụta ma ọbu mmepe no na Lagos, in Steeti Lagos , Naijiria a Local Council Development Area (LCDA) no na mpaghara Oshodi-Isolo local government area.
na afọ 2009, onye nnọchiteanya ányá onye isi oche,  bu onye ana akpọ Hon
